WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
[Description] The presenter appears on screen in front of the game Hogwarts Legacy. He starts speaking in an animated tone.

00:10.000 --> 00:17.000
[Description] In the game, the character casts the Revelio spell. Bright objects with question mark symbols appear.

00:17.000 --> 00:19.000
[Description] The character moves through different rooms in search of the objects.

00:19.000 --> 00:25.000
[Description] The character approaches a mysterious door and presses a button to display a sequence of numbers and symbols.

00:25.000 --> 00:29.000
[Description] The numbers 5 and 12 appear on the door's mechanism.

00:29.000 --> 00:33.000
[Description] The presenter zooms in on the door to explain the number puzzle.

00:33.000 --> 00:41.000
[Description] A triangle with numbers and symbols at its vertices appears on the screen.

00:41.000 --> 00:46.000
[Description] A guide is shown with the game's symbols and their corresponding numerical values from 0 to 9.

00:46.000 --> 00:50.000
[Description] The presenter points to the symbols and explains how values are assigned to each.

00:51.000 --> 00:55.000
[Description] The first puzzle is solved by adding the values: 3 + 0 + 2.

00:55.000 --> 00:58.000
[Description] A symbol in the shape of a goat is selected as the answer.

00:58.000 --> 01:00.000
[Description] The cursor highlights the symbols in order: 0, 1, 2.

01:00.000 --> 01:02.000
[Description] It is confirmed that the sum matches the target number.

01:02.000 --> 01:08.000
[Description] The character spins the object with a question mark and selects the correct symbol.

01:08.000 --> 01:12.000
[Description] The second puzzle is tackled, which results in the number 12.

01:12.000 --> 01:13.000
[Description] The cursor moves to the symbol already visible on the screen.

01:13.000 --> 01:16.000
[Description] The symbol shown is the unicorn, identified as value 1.

01:16.000 --> 01:18.000
[Description] The presenter continues explaining the logic behind the puzzle.

01:18.000 --> 01:25.000
[Description] The values 1 + 4 + 7 are added, and the symbol in the shape of an octopus is selected.

01:25.000 --> 01:30.000
[Description] The character interacts with the second spinning object and picks the correct symbol.

01:32.000 --> 01:36.000
[Description] The character stands in front of the door and presses the button to open it.

01:36.000 --> 01:41.000
[Description] The door slowly opens, revealing a secret room with a glowing chest inside.
